      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_MoveRawDataIntoCurrentBillingCycleBatchFile",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to execute a batch file that moves raw data into the current billing cycle directory. It retrieves the current fiscal year and billing period from the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing.ApplicationTimeFrame",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table where the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "CurrentProcessingPeriod",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is marked as 'Y'. The procedure then constructs a command string to execute a batch file located on a network share, passing the fiscal year and billing period as arguments. The procedure temporarily enables the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "xp_cmdshell",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " feature to execute the command and then disables it afterward."
        }
      ]
    },
