      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure is relatively straightforward, involving basic SQL operations such as variable declaration, data retrieval, and command execution. The complexity arises mainly from the use of "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "xp_cmdshell",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", which requires careful handling due to security implications."
        }
      ]
    },
